com.mk4droid.IMC_Store
Class Constants

java.lang.Object
  com.mk4droid.IMC_Store.Constants

public class Constants
extends java.lang.Object

Constants visible everywhere in the app. Customization for your application is feasible. HINT: Be careful when to use http:// or https:// in downloading and uploading data. It highly depends on your platform HINT2: Be careful with the paths of your remote server. Paths may differ per implementation.

Author:
Dimitrios Ververidis, Dr. Post-doctoral Researcher, Information Technologies Institute, ITI-CERTH, Thermi, Thessaloniki, Greece ververid@iti.gr, http://mklab.iti.gr
